{"tid":557673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺搭車爭贏位嗰種感覺好正","createTime":"2018-02-11T14:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T16:03:05.000Z","uid":62277,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5f59b9a690f686d463a1ca914ae5ac2e458aa6","tid":557673,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"發覺而家d後生仔好捱得,搭車鍾意見企<br />\n所以d對手多數都係廢中廢老<br />\n佢地蠢到仆街,上到車先慢慢揾位<br />\n多數都會輸俾我<br />\n因為我會喺㗎車慢慢埋緊站時<br />\n就望定所有剩餘座位既位置<br />\n見到佢地發現自己慢一步失望撤退個様真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最爽就係<br />\n喺搭長途巴士嗰陣<br />\n有時架車幾滿,下層得返幾個位<br />\n上層情況未知<br />\n排隊排我前面嗰幾個仲走上樓上搏<br />\n俾我坐埋最後最後嗰個位<br />\n見到佢地喺上面落返黎<br />\n由明明有位變無<br />\n成隻死狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bba0398d7b5849db5caa6c1bb249b2c162fe4e6","tid":557673,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔係後生鍾意企,而係無得坐"},{"pid":"c3931e3bb34ef5a091d5ee29008c2fdbeb1495e3","tid":557673,"uid":152006,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"乜依家啲廢老/大媽都識上連登開post㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be8620bf12650fd699249fb6a63baea246065a1","tid":557673,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af20816c2abe136d427f6dd96ea84e543265650c","tid":557673,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"唔係爭贏個感覺正<br />\n係睇d廢老冇得坐個失望樣正啫<img src=\"/assets/fa